    "updated_at": "2014-08-01T01:24:07Z",
    "body": "The '--remote-debugging-port' is supported in brightray [2f87b8](https://github.com/brightray/brightray/commit/2f87b814ac97eb52628f0808842c99df0611a86e), and the commit of brightray in atom-shell v0.15.1 is [91a5af](https://github.com/brightray/brightray/commit/91a5af92231458009165a853e279192acdca947c) which is earlier. So in v0.15.1 this feature is not supported.\n"
